formation via e-mail to: jobs@orl.bc.ca. We thank all applicants for their interest in our organization; however, only short-listed applicants will be contacted.Competition Number: 24-104 Compensation $83,880 to $89,226​ per year. Closes: 13 November, 2024 Okanagan Regional Library Kelowna , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
