o $96,549 per year. Please visit out website at http://www.orl.bc.ca/careers/current-vacancies for the job description.Please forward a covering letter, a resume, and reference via e-mail to: jobs@orl.bc.ca. We thank all applicants for their interest in our organization; however, only short-listed applicants will be contacted. Competition Number: 24-102 Compensation $90,154 - $96,549. per year Closes: 15 September, 2024 Okanagan Regional Library Kelowna , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
